## 📄 File 6: `docs/digest/index.html`

### Design Brief
- **Aesthetic:** Dark, terminal-intelligence. Like a war room screen. Deep navy/black background, amber/gold accents, monospace display font for data, clean sans-serif for body.
- **Layout:** Full-width header with top story. Below: 5 collapsible section cards in a 2-column grid. Timestamp top-right. Password gate on load.
- **Fonts:** `JetBrains Mono` (display/headers) + `DM Sans` (body) — both from Google Fonts.
- **Motion:** Cards fade+slide in on load, staggered. Sections expand smoothly on click.
- **Password:** Hardcoded string `"dads42digest"` — stored in localStorage so you only enter once per browser.
- **Data source:** Fetches `./data.json` on load (same directory, works on GitHub Pages).
- **Mobile:** Single column below 768px.
- **No frameworks. No build step. Pure HTML/CSS/JS.**

